          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>The oval cut has become one of the most sought-after shapes in modern jewellery. It offers the brilliance of a round stone with a more distinctive and elegant silhouette.⁠</p><ul><li>A soft, elongated shape that flatters the<br/>finger</li><li>Appears larger than many other cuts of the<br/>same size⁠</li><li>A modern yet timeless alternative to round<br/>stones⁠</li><li>Perfect for those looking for elegant promise<br/>rings for her</li></ul><p>Oval promise rings are often chosen by those<br/>who want something classic, but with a slightly more contemporary feel.</p><p>A balance of elegance and individuality. Oval promise rings strike a unique balance between traditional and modern design. While they share the brilliance of classic cuts, their shape adds a subtle individuality that sets them apart.</p><p>This makes them a popular choice for people who want a ring that feels<br/>timeless, but still slightly different. The oval cut offers a softer, more fluid look compared to sharper shapes, making it ideal for everyday wear while still feeling special.</p>"
          }
